#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:3
msgid "Synchronizing with iOS"
msgstr "Synkronisera med iOS"

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:6
msgid "Calendar"
msgstr "Kalender"

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:8 ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:37
msgid "Open the settings application."
msgstr "Öppna appen Inställningar."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:9 ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:38
msgid "Select Apps."
msgstr "Välj Appar."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:10
msgid "Select Calendar."
msgstr "Välj Kalender."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:11
msgid "Select Calendar Accounts."
msgstr "Välj Kalenderkonton."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:12 ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:41
msgid "Select Add Account."
msgstr "Välj Lägg till konto."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:13 ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:42
msgid "Select Other as account type."
msgstr "Välj Annat som kontotyp."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:14
msgid "Select Add CalDAV account."
msgstr "Välj Lägg till CalDAV-konto."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:15
msgid "For server, type the domain name of your server i.e. ``example.com``."
msgstr ""
"För servern anger du serverns domännamn, till exempel ``example.com``."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:16 ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:45
msgid "Enter your user name and password."
msgstr "Ange ditt användarnamn och lösenord."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:17 ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:46
msgid "Select Next."
msgstr "Välj Nästa."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:18
msgid "Open Advanced Settings"
msgstr "Öppna Avancerade inställningar"

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:19 ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:44
msgid ""
"For server, type the domain name of your server and path, i.e., "
"``example.com/remote.php/dav/principals/users/username/`` (replace "
"**example.com** and **username**)."
msgstr ""
"För servern anger du serverns domännamn och sökväg, till exempel "
"``example.com/remote.php/dav/principals/users/username/`` (ersätt "
"**example.com** och **username** med dina värden)."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:20
msgid "Close Advanced Settings"
msgstr "Stäng Avancerade inställningar"

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:22
msgid "Your calendar will now be visible in the Calendar application."
msgstr "Din kalender visas nu i appen Kalender."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:24
msgid ""
"If you get an error message related to SSL, you can try the following: Make "
"sure that you either specify both the protocol (``https://``) and the port "
"(usually ``443``) in the ``Server`` field, i.e., "
"``https://example.com:443/remote.php/dav/principals/users/username/``, or "
"none, like in the step-by-step guide above. Either way, the application "
"automatically tries to use SSL, which you can confirm in  “Advanced "
"Settings” of the account after saving."
msgstr ""
"Om du får ett SSL-relaterat felmeddelande kan du prova följande: Se till att"
" du antingen anger både protokollet (``https://``) och porten (vanligen "
"``443``) i fältet ``Server``, till exempel "
"``https://example.com:443/remote.php/dav/principals/users/username/``, eller"
" inte anger något av dem, som i steg-för-steg-anvisningen ovan. Appen "
"försöker i båda fallen automatiskt använda SSL, vilket du kan kontrollera "
"under ”Avancerade inställningar” för kontot efter att du har sparat det."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:30 ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:50
msgid ""
"Beginning with iOS 12 an SSL encryption is necessary. Therefore do **not** "
"disable **SSL** (For this reason a certificate is required at your domain, "
"https://letsencrypt.org/ will do)."
msgstr ""
"Från och med iOS 12 krävs SSL-kryptering. **Inaktivera därför inte** **SSL**"
" (av den anledningen krävs ett certifikat för din domän; "
"https://letsencrypt.org/ fungerar)."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:35
msgid "Contacts"
msgstr "Kontakter"

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:39
msgid "Select Contacts."
msgstr "Välj Kontakter."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:40
msgid "Select Contacts Accounts."
msgstr "Välj Kontaktkonton."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:43
msgid "Select Add CardDAV account."
msgstr "Välj Lägg till CardDAV-konto."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:48
msgid "You should now find your contacts in the address book of your iPhone."
msgstr "Du bör nu hitta dina kontakter i adressboken på din iPhone."

#: ../../groupware/sync_ios.rst:54
msgid ""
"If it's still not working, have a look at `Troubleshooting Contacts & "
"Calendar`_ or `Troubleshooting Service Discovery`_."
msgstr ""
"Om det fortfarande inte fungerar kan du läsa `Troubleshooting Contacts & "
"Calendar`_ eller `Troubleshooting Service Discovery`_."
